mit on H.R. 3898, H.R. 3383, H.R. 3638, H.R. 3628, and H.R. 3668; and one motion to commit on S. 1071.", "date": "2025-12-10T00:52:18+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Placed on the Union Calendar, Calendar No. 145.", "date": "2025-07-02T04:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Reported (Amended) by the Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure. H. Rept. 119-180.", "date": "2025-07-02T04:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Ordered to be Reported (Amended) by the Yeas and Nays: 34 - 30.", "date": "2025-06-25T04:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Committee Consideration and Mark-up Session Held", "date": "2025-06-25T04:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Subcommittee on Water Resources and Environment Discharged", "date": "2025-06-25T04:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Referred to the Subcommittee on Water Resources and Environment.", "date": "2025-06-13T04:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Referred to the House Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure.", "date": "2025-06-11T04:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Introduced in House", "date": "2025-06-11T04:00:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["introduction"], "related_entitie